{"tid":1612903,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我都都想要黃絲家人，我都想有家人支持","createTime":"2019-10-02T11:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T12:13:16.000Z","uid":26087,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"bac8a56aaeced9240b95003f79f797274d829a96","tid":1612903,"uid":26087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:33:30.000Z","msg":"琴晚上前線，見到有手足家人陪佢去佢地係後面support個仔，我同個手足比煙入到隻眼去後邊洗，見到人地有呀媽即刻幫佢拎生理鹽水洗眼，叫佢有咩事記得跑要小心而我就自己一個洗，果陣見到個真係覺得好羨慕。<br />\n<br />\n我唔係希望我屋企人肯陪我上前線一齊捱，只係希望你地唔好係到鬧出面啲o靚仔有，只係想你地有番人應該有嘅良知。你個仔都係出面打緊仲要仆街差啲比人拉只係好彩比人救左。<br />\n<br />\n琴晚佢地仲要睇閱兵唱國歌，好撚辛苦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ad2861346940dfe17cdcb52c91b198c07b63d85","tid":1612903,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:34:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33733077425730af9cc237a6120fd54d92f10332","tid":1612903,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:34:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5badd2ad7fd8db67a27609874f185977bfb88e2b","tid":1612903,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:35:25.000Z","msg":"摸頭"},{"pid":"6fa29472f2894fd5ff87bb5e6c299139aa340128","tid":1612903,"uid":26087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"33733077425730af9cc237a6120fd54d92f10332","tid":1612903,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:34:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:38:02.000Z","msg":"已經無係屋企講野，家姐叫我當睇唔到，全屋得家姐係黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf12493ac867342cfe8e06d57dcecdce92bcc38","tid":1612903,"uid":28921,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:38:14.000Z","msg":"我永遠支持你嫁樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得閒tg下啦<br />\n<br />\nbtw有個勇武既老母都好撚擔心<br />\n每次發夢都分開，老人家唔識用tg果d收風，真係好擔心，次次打俾佢都話望多陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" cl